                {"swissGerman": "Bsuech gha", "german": "Besuch gehabt", "explanation": "'Bsuech' = 'Besuch', 'gha' = 'gehabt'. Perfekt tense as always."},
                {"swissGerman": "Bescheid gäh", "german": "Bescheid geben", "explanation": "'gäh' = 'geben'. Common vowel shift."},
